                            <comment id="12809562" author="dmlloyd" created="Fri, 4 Oct 2013 14:38:28 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you try the alternative fix in the last commit of &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/dmlloyd/wildfly/tree/WFLY-2222&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/dmlloyd/wildfly/tree/WFLY-2222&lt;/a&gt; which hopefully will solve the same problem but without holding the synch over the duration of the doPrivileged?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12809564" author="fluetm" created="Fri, 4 Oct 2013 14:57:05 -0400"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure...we will setup our patched server with this alternative fix and let the automated restarts continue over the weekend.  Will report status back here on Monday.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
